kgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"729017b7e09dc3291b351cb953517130ab516984","tid":432181,"uid":8767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T02:03:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鐘意睇劇情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反而真正扑個陣就飛住黎睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原來唔係淨係得我係噉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n尤其係人妻被姦嘅劇情，之後中間諗起被姦就會自己捽碟，最後忍唔住叫個姦夫黎扑自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  睇極都唔厭"}]}